					), or increased with distance from the soma (
					), consistent with observations in several brain areas [14,18,19]. Slopes and intercepts of conductance densities are shown in the top of Figure 1E. Backpropagation of somatic APs into the dendrite, as a result of these dendritic distributions, is shown at the bottom of Figure 1E. Compare profiles of the somatic AP (red trace) with the AP as it backpropagates through the dendrite (black traces).
